00:57:03,211 --> 00:57:05,155
<i>Es personal.</i>

890
00:57:05,255 --> 00:57:08,116
SERÁN RECORDADOS

891
00:57:08,216 --> 00:57:11,015
<i>Así que nos reunimos para orar
